Comment: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:33.67,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:213677,213677}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215311,216513}Jules.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216513,218715}No matter the result\Nof your duel with Victor,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218715,221885}I cannot approve of you\Nbeing my daughter's husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222652,226723}The Rostain family\Nis a family of a high social status.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227223,230694}You have left a stain\Non our family's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231327,234330}But Mr. Jules risked his life\Nfor my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234330,236032}Silence, Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236032,238034}This is adults talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:03:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238034,239169}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239169,240570}It's fine, Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241337,244541}Father, I want to live\Ntogether with Jules.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244541,246142}I am ready for consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246409,247644}– You stupid girl!\N– Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249379,251014}You're terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251014,252816}You're terrible, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263026,264594}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264594,267897}Geneviève.\NI will no longer attempt to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267897,271568}From now on, you are\Nno longer a part of this family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272969,274871}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274871,275872}Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276339,278041}Do not call me your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284581,287250}Marie. Don't be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287250,289452}The Geneviève we knew is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289452,293089}Our only children are now\NAndréa and Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.72,0:04:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294724,297794}Master, the preparations\Nfor the departure are all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:05:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298895,300530}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300530,303399}All right. It is time, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309906,312942}Everyone go ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318581,324154}{\i1}Did I raise her wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326756,328424}{\i1}Geneviève.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330727,332996}{\i1}You were such a kind child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451147,452982}Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452982,454717}Everyone is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458488,459589}Gaston.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459589,460390}Yes, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460390,461925}There is something\NI would like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461925,464794}I would like to release you\Nfrom serving our family as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464794,468131}Yes, Master.\NI can't say I didn't see it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471734,473603}Take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473603,475138}What is inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475138,479809}I have one more favor to ask.\NPlease watch over Geneviève for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479809,483947}Very difficult times are coming.\NUse this money to support her in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483947,485415}I know I am asking a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486349,488785}Can you grant my wish\Nnonetheless?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488785,490753}Yes, Master.\NI shall grant your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492021,493723}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494424,500296}To begin with, I was devoted\Nto Ms. Geneviève the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524787,526990}Andréa, I'm leaving\Nthe rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527390,529158}Yes, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529158,530360}Don't worry about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532095,533329}Andréa…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534664,536733}I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536733,538801}I am not going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538801,540770}Sister…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540770,542538}Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542538,544874}All right, we're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551881,552615}Gaston.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557286,557887}Hyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567263,568064}Geneviève!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574537,575571}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575571,576372}Geneviève.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578007,579876}{\i1}Sister…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585181,589185}Listen, Geneviève. This is the path\Nyou've chosen for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589185,591954}Do not look away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591954,594924}You can't take back\Nwhat you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617814,622018}{\i1}Later this afternoon,\NJules and Geneviève
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622018,627256}{\i1}had a low-key wedding ceremony\Nat a small church in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627757,632095}In the name of the Lord Almighty,\NI now pronounce you husband and wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632762,633963}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651280,654050}Jules, I won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654050,655084}Take care of my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656018,657987}Andréa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:10:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657987,659288}Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:659722,661858}You got what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661858,663326}Cherish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663726,665928}Thank you, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666195,667897}Jules.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667897,669565}There's one thing\NI fail to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669565,670433}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670433,672702}I mean your lovely bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672702,675371}Even though she just lost it all:\Nthe land, the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675371,677340}she looks so happy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679909,681244}That's a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682044,683613}Andréa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685081,686015}Victor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691554,693189}I've been looking\Nfor you, Andréa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703299,706102}I am sorry to disturb the harmony\Nof this occasion, but it is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706102,708471}The Prussian army\Nhas started surrounding Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708471,710039}What? So fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710039,712108}Damn it!\NVictor, give me your horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712375,713643}Hm? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713643,716412}My family is on their way\Nto Versailles right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716412,718281}They might come across\Nthe enemy troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:12:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718514,720149}I understand.\NI will go warn them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720416,723586}No, it is too dangerous.\NI will take care of my family by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723586,725221}Give me your horse. Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727323,729058}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736499,737433}Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740203,742505}You are beyond belief.
Comment: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:39.85,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:759855,759855}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793122,798828}{\i1}The Prussian army started\Nto encircle the city of Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798828,802031}{\i1}As the Rostain family\Nwas heading to Versailles,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802031,805201}{\i1}many of the Prussian troops were\Nalready in the area, waiting for refugees.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805701,807570}{\i1}However, the Rostains\Ndid not know about it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813142,815878}Hi! It's me, Jean,\Nwith my daily marriage proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815878,817546}Homesick already, Isabelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818514,820950}Geez, stop following me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820950,822885}The sight of your face\Nmakes me nauseous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823252,825221}Come on, before long,\Nyou'll get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825221,828090}And once you do, it's in the bag.\NI can already hear the church bells!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828090,830159}Tin-tan-din-dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.15,0:13:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830159,833062}My taste is not nearly bad enough\Nto get used to your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833062,836098}Oh, I wouldn't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:14:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836098,841504}You see, from now on, I'll follow you\Nwherever you go, like a shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841904,843906}Oh, is that right?\NLike a shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843906,849045}Shadows do not blabber as much\Nand do not keep sending unwanted flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849045,850279}Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850279,852715}Another rejection today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852715,854216}Today and tomorrow, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854216,858354}Oh, whatever. If I hold out long enough,\Nyou'll grow to love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858354,859221}Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:859221,860289}Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861057,862124}I can't believe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870866,872702}What was that?\NWhat is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873269,877940}Master, it seems we have entered\Nright into middle of a battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877940,879241}What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879241,880576}Stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885247,888317}We will cross that bridge,\Nthen we will go into the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888551,889685}Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889685,890753}Hyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:929625,930993}Mother!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930993,931961}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931961,933596}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951614,954450}We should be\Nat a safe distance here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955518,956786}Where is Isabelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956786,958287}I can't see\Nher carriage anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:15:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958621,959622}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966962,968898}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969265,971100}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971467,973102}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973369,974804}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975204,977440}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979642,980943}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981610,982845}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982945,983879}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984280,985614}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.01,0:16:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987016,990186}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994056,995758}Victor! Jean!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996425,997426}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999829,1001397}Isabelle…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004800,1006669}Isabelle, hang on to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010005,1010940}Are you okay, Isabelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010940,1012007}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012341,1014577}Geez, Victor again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014577,1016712}Why is he always interfering?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:17:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016712,1021383}Hey, buddy!\NWe must have a little chat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022952,1025754}On second thought,\Nwe can do that later. Hyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055117,1057219}Not good.\NThey blew up the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081577,1083512}What about the rest\Nof the Rostains?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083512,1086682}Well, they did cross the bridge.\NI think they'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086682,1088551}They're probably\Nin Versailles by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090619,1093155}Thank goodness.\NWhat are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093956,1096125}The road to Versailles\Nis swarming with enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096125,1098327}Going back to Paris\Nseems to be our only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098327,1100362}The way home\Nis full of enemies, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100362,1104099}If we go on foot,\Nwe'll get caught sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104667,1106201}It'll be fine, Jean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106201,1107436}Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129458,1131060}– What was that?\N– Not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142504,1143672}This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148310,1149044}There's a guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156118,1157486}There's a cart.\NWe'll snatch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161890,1163058}Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171333,1172267}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178507,1181110}Damn! Take this, you oaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185581,1186515}Jean!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189351,1192187}Damn! Don't think you can mock me\Njust because you're big!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200362,1201163}Jean!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201997,1204099}Now you've done it, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215244,1217046}You're so pathetic, Jean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217046,1220049}You can't do\N{\i1}anything{\i0} without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221050,1222951}I won't deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223686,1225020}Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226422,1228390}Hands up, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231493,1232828}Victor…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232828,1234897}Jean, you take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235564,1237299}All right, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242104,1243038}Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.74,0:20:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248744,1249311}Hyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254850,1256318}After them!\NDon't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269031,1270265}Isabelle, can you drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271333,1272167}I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272735,1274069}Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277706,1279942}You can't shoot\Nrandomly like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1279942,1283312}Lean slightly forward.\NLet your body absorb the recoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293689,1296391}You don't need to aim at people.\NHorses are enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297059,1298260}Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1304800,1307369}Mr. Victor,\Nyour wound from the duel…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1308504,1311306}Now's not the time for that.\NShoot. Keep shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:21:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316879,1317646}You're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.61,0:22:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321617,1322551}Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322885,1325254}Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.01,0:22:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1355017,1356318}It's our friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.31,0:22:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1356318,1357419}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1367396,1372701}{\i1}The moment Isabelle had realized\Nthey were safe, she fainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1374536,1375704}{\i1}Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.71,0:23:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1382711,1384313}You saved our skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.81,0:23:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1385814,1387182}Are you okay, Victor?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.98,0:23:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1387983,1390052}Yes. All thanks to little Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.55,0:23:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1392554,1396024}Let's get her to a carriage\Nsuitable for a lady like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.79,0:23:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1398794,1400429}Such a cute face.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1400429,1402331}You're still just a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.10,0:23:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1408103,1410505}Ah, there he goes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1410505,1412741}Why does Victor\Nalways look so cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.91,0:23:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1417913,1422351}{\i1}Even though she was carried\Nby the person she longed for…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.28,0:23:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1423285,1427222}{\i1}Isabelle remained unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.19,0:23:57.16,Credits,[credits],0,0,0,,{TIME:1432194,1437165}{\fad(200,50)\c&HFAFAFA&\blur1\fs17\an5\pos(511,362)}To be continued
Comment: 0,0:23:57.49,0:23:57.49,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1437499,1437499}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.49,0:24:00.46,Default,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1437499,1440469}Next episode preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.60,0:24:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1441603,1445474}General Gambetta heads to Versailles\Nin a hot-air balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.47,0:24:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1445474,1448277}Thanks to my brother's position,\NI get to fly with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.67,0:24:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1448677,1452881}Ah! Soon I'll be able\Nto meet Mother and Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.88,0:24:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1452881,1454816}Mr. Victor is flying with us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.81,0:24:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1454816,1456885}And so is Jean.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.88,0:24:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1456885,1458287}The danger lurks everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.28,0:24:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1458287,1461423}I wonder if we can get\Nto Versailles safely?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.42,0:24:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1461423,1463725}Next time on "Isabelle from Paris":
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.72,0:24:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1463725,1467496}"Escape in a Hot-air Balloon".\NPlease look forward to it.
